---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/site-layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy at LLCAtlas';
const description =
  "How this site handles your data. Short version: it doesn't collect any.";
const pageUrl = 'https://llcatlas.com/privacy/';
const lastUpdated = 'April 2026';

const structuredData = [
  {
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'WebPage',
    name: title,
    description,
    url: pageUrl,
    inLanguage: 'en-US',
  },
];
---

<SiteLayout title={title} description={description} structuredData={structuredData}>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      Last updated {lastUpdated}. This site doesn't track you. Here's what that actually looks
      like.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="what-we-collect" class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
    <h2 id="what-we-collect">What we collect</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      We use <a
        href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="font-semibold text-ink-strong underline decoration-rule-strong underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-ink-soft hover:decoration-ink-muted"
      >Cloudflare Web Analytics</a> to count visits to each page. It doesn't use cookies. It
      doesn't try to figure out who you are. It counts pageviews and where the visit came from,
      and that's it.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      That's the only analytics on this site. No Google Analytics. No Facebook pixel. No session
      replay. No ad networks.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="how-we-earn" class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
    <h2 id="how-we-earn">How this site makes money</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      Some of the outbound links here are affiliate links. If you click one and sign up with a
      formation service like Northwest, Bizee, or LegalZoom, we earn a small commission. You pay
      the same price either way.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      The commission doesn't change which service we recommend. We recommend the cheapest good
      option first and the safest paid option second, and we say so whether anyone is paying us
      or not. If a service stops paying affiliates tomorrow, our recommendations wouldn't change.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      We don't run display ads. No banners, no pop-ups, no sponsored articles written to look
      like reviews.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="cookies" class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
    <h2 id="cookies">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      We don't set cookies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="your-data" class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
    <h2 id="your-data">Your data</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      We don't collect personal information from you, so there's nothing to export and nothing
      to delete. Nothing to opt out of either.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      If that ever changes, for example if we add a newsletter or a login, we'll say so on this
      page before collecting anything.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="changes" class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
    <h2 id="changes">Changes to this page</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-ink-soft">
      If we change what we collect, we'll update the date at the top and explain what changed.
      We won't bury anything.
    </p>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
